This paper deals with the capacity of a multihop relay channel, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of relays and optimization techniques, which are relevant to systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions wireless backhaul, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography (cs.CR) categories.
